nodes.text: The Chieftain's Canopy was an area situated at the top of the Origin Tree on the planet Kashyyyk. Long before the Imperial Era, the Zeffo visited Kashyyyk, and left an Astrium in the Chieftain's Canopy. The Jedi Master Eno Cordova, guided by the Wookiee chieftain Tarfful, climbed the tree and retrieved the Astrium. A number of years later, the former Jedi Padawan Cal Kestis retraced Cordova's steps.
